@startuml seq-10-publish-work
' 序列图10：发布作品
title 发布作品序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "publish.js" as Front
participant "UploadController" as UpCtrl
participant "UserWorkController" as Ctrl
participant "UserWorkService" as Svc
participant "UserWorkMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 选择多张图片
Front -> UpCtrl: POST /api/upload(多图)
UpCtrl -> UpCtrl: 生成UUID文件名
UpCtrl -> UpCtrl: 写入uploads/yyyy-MM-dd/
UpCtrl --> Front: [/uploads/.../xxx.jpg, ...]
User -> Front: 填写标题/分类/内容,点击发布
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/work/publish(userId,title,images,categoryId)
Ctrl -> Svc: publish(userWork)
Svc -> Mapper: insert(userWork)
Mapper -> DB: INSERT INTO user_work
DB --> Mapper: work_id
Mapper --> Svc: work_id
Svc --> Ctrl: work_id
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200}
Front --> User: 提示发布成功,跳转作品列表

@enduml
